---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const pageTitle = 'Deliveries and Returns';
const pageDescription = 'Information about delivery costs, carriers, delivery times and returns policy at Hercules Merchandise UK.';
---

<BaseLayout
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
  pageType="page"
>
  <!-- Breadcrumb -->
  <section class="breadcrumb-section">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <ol itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/BreadcrumbList">
          <li itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
            <a href="/" itemprop="item">
              <span itemprop="name">Home</span>
            </a>
            <meta itemprop="position" content="1" />
            <span class="separator"><img src="/images/breadcrumb-separator.svg" alt="" width="6" height="12" /></span>
          </li>
          <li itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
            <span itemprop="name">Deliveries and Returns</span>
            <meta itemprop="position" content="2" />
          </li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <h1>Deliveries and Returns</h1>

        <div class="content-card">
          <div class="qa-item">
            <h2>A. What are the delivery costs?</h2>
            <p>Shipping costs for delivery to the UK and Ireland are included in the prices mentioned on our website (unless otherwise stated). For other countries, please contact us. Express delivery is available for most items.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="qa-item">
            <h2>B. Which carriers do you use?</h2>
            <p>The carrier depends on the item ordered and the factory shipping the package. We use several carriers such as FedEx, UPS or DHL.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="qa-item">
            <h2>C. What is the delivery time?</h2>
            <p>Standard shipments take approximately one week, while express shipments arrive within 24 or 48 hours.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="qa-item">
            <h2>D. Returns</h2>
            <p>If you are dissatisfied with your purchase, you have 14 days from the date of receipt to initiate a return. Manufacturing defects will result in item replacement. However, it is not possible to return a custom-made item, except in the case of a production error!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .breadcrumb-section {
    background: #FAFAFA;
    padding: 15px 0;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .breadcrumb ol {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .breadcrumb li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .breadcrumb a {
    color: #787878;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .breadcrumb a:hover {
    color: #469ADC;
  }

  .breadcrumb li:last-child span {
    color: #469ADC;
  }

  .breadcrumb .separator {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .page-section {
    background: #FAFAFA;
    padding: 40px 0 80px;
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #253461;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .content-card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 50px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .qa-item {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    padding-bottom: 30px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #E8E8E8;
  }

  .qa-item:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .qa-item h2 {
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #253461;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
  }

  .qa-item p {
    font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #5F5F5F;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .content-card {
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }

    .qa-item h2 {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
  }
</style>
